reviews.text: Something I must have once in a while. The price is very attractive at promo times. The young lady cashier is very cheerful and upbeat!

Perfect snack for killing any blues after a tough day. Super tasty and super convenient! There is a reason why they have more than 16000 outlets globally.

Get their cuttle fish at half price ($6 instead of $12) from their website! From now till 31st May.

Spend above $100 on their website and you get free delivery island wide. Quote "mayvip" to enjoy 10% off!

2 more weeks left for the promo. Head on to their website now!

https://www.juewei.com.sg
